        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Beds: 1 Baths: 1 Square Feet: 693 Want more information? Follow this link: https://amc.touraptnow.com/7bup5o Sundance Apartments in Cheyenne, WY: Live Seconds From Shopping, Dining, Arts & Culture. Call Now - show contact info x 83 OR Text 83 to show contact info to contact our team.   Community Info Sundance Apartments in Cheyenne, WY, offers you your dream lifestyle. Experience the convenience of a home with the benefits of a great location and the comfort of knowing our community was built with quality and contemporary living in mind. In addition to a thriving neighborhood, you'll have close access to shopping, dining, parks, adventure, and local entertainment. Spend weekends exploring the natural world close to home at Holliday Park or meet up with friends at Cheyenne Country Club or Botanic Gardens. Make the most of our location near all the area has to offer. Start the day with Omelet House or Paramount Cafe, finish it with Hambones Pizza or Black Tooth Brewing, and then come home to Sundance Apartments where you'll find plenty of space to call your own. Step into a life of ease and modern living with our friendly community. Contact us today! Residence Features ✩  Carpeting ✩  Wheelchair Access ✩  Air Conditioner ✩  Walk In Closets ✩  Ceiling Fans ✩  Window Covering ✩  Balcony/Patio ✩  Dishwasher ✩  Full Size Washer & Dryer ✩  High Ceilings ✩  Refrigerator ✩  Open Concept Floor Plan ✩  Microwave ✩  Vinyl Plank Flooring Community Features ✩  Indoor Hot Tub ✩  Playground ✩  Convenient Location ✩  Garages Available ✩  Picnic Area ✩  Covered Parking ✩  24 Hours Fitness Center ✩  Basketball Court ✩  Swimming Pool ✩  On-Site Maintenance ✩  Professional & Responsive Management Pet Policy At Sundance Apartments WY in Cheyenne, we love your pets just as much as you do! Because of that, Sundance Apartments WY is not just a pet-friendly property, but a pet-enthusiastic property. Your pets will find just as inviting a home here as you will. Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply. Equal Housing Opportunity ot6S0tPiJkY",
