        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Beds: 1 Baths: 1 Square Feet: 693 Want more info? See the link below: https://amc.touraptnow.com/hbodwv Sundance Apartments in Cheyenne, WY: Live Seconds From Shopping, Dining, Arts & Culture. Call Now - show contact info x 75 OR Text 75 to show contact info for more information.   Community Info Sundance Apartments in Cheyenne, WY, offers you your dream lifestyle. Experience the convenience of a home with the benefits of a great location and the comfort of knowing our community was built with quality and contemporary living in mind. In addition to a thriving neighborhood, you'll have close access to shopping, dining, parks, adventure, and local entertainment. Spend weekends exploring the natural world close to home at Holliday Park or meet up with friends at Cheyenne Country Club or Botanic Gardens. Make the most of our location near all the area has to offer. Start the day with Omelet House or Paramount Cafe, finish it with Hambones Pizza or Black Tooth Brewing, and then come home to Sundance Apartments where you'll find plenty of space to call your own. Step into a life of ease and modern living with our friendly community. Contact us today! Residence Features ✩  Air Conditioner ✩  High Ceilings ✩  Window Covering ✩  Vinyl Plank Flooring ✩  Walk In Closets ✩  Full Size Washer & Dryer ✩  Microwave ✩  Carpeting ✩  Ceiling Fans ✩  Dishwasher ✩  Wheelchair Access ✩  Open Concept Floor Plan ✩  Balcony/Patio ✩  Refrigerator Community Features ✩  Basketball Court ✩  Picnic Area ✩  Covered Parking ✩  Professional & Responsive Management ✩  On-Site Maintenance ✩  Convenient Location ✩  24 Hours Fitness Center ✩  Garages Available ✩  Playground ✩  Indoor Hot Tub ✩  Swimming Pool Pet Policy At Sundance Apartments WY in Cheyenne, we love your pets just as much as you do! Because of that, Sundance Apartments WY is not just a pet-friendly property, but a pet-enthusiastic property. Your pets will find just as inviting a home here as you will. Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply. Equal Housing Opportunity lio2joyVSmw",
